    "Implementation.",
    "We implement SHIP based on the official GitHub repository of paper (Huang et al., 2023a).",
    "We use QLoRA with a rank of 64 and an alpha of 256, training for 4 epochs with a learning rate of 0.0002.",
    "The weights and activations are quantized to 4 bits.",
    "Overall, training on one sample takes 0.23s and evaluate on one sample takes 0.09s on two NVIDIA A6000 GPUs."
